Compilation:

# Compile the ocaml library to an object file
./compile_ml

# Compile to a dynamic shared library (libocamlsearchr.so)
./compile_c

# Compile the library to interface with ruby to a dynamic shared library (librubyocamlsearchr.so)
./compile_ruby

Examples:

With the C library:
./compile_exc
LD_LIBRARY_PATH="." ./exc

With the ruby library:
LD_LIBRARY_PATH="." ruby exruby.rb

Clean:

# Clean all the files and examples
./clean
